V0203_01_00_00_0.text:
I heard you were looking for me.
Looks like you succeeded.

V0203_01_00_01_0.text:
Watch me, kids!
I'll show you jackals how to Duel!

V0203_01_00_02_0.text:
You're yearnin' to Duel?
Cool! Let's get it on!

V0203_01_00_03_0.text:
Bring it on!
You'll see how tough my Blackwings are!

V0203_01_00_04_0.text: Just cuz you're my buddy doesn't mean I'll go easy on ya!

V0203_01_00_05_0.text:
Aww, you suffered through some tough times?
Who hasn't?

V0203_01_00_06_0.text: I don't care if you're a Signer or not!

V0203_01_00_06_1.text: All I care about is slammin' your brakes!

V0203_01_00_07_0.text: This Duel won't go as you think!

V0203_01_00_07_1.text:
I know I can defeat ya!
Cuz when I fight, I FIGHT!

V0203_03_00_00_0.text: I still got a lot more in the tank!

V0203_03_00_01_0.text: I know you see your end comin'!

V0203_03_00_04_0.text: You haven't broken our bond yet!

V0203_03_00_05_0.text: Man, my gas is runnin' out...

V0203_05_00_00_0.text:
It all depends on this draw...
But I believe in my deck!

V0203_06_01_02_0.text: You think that'll work against me?

V0203_06_01_03_0.text: I was waiting for you to do that!

V0203_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my face-down card!

V0203_08_00_07_0.text: Here's my Equip Spell, Glow Wing Crossbow!

V0203_08_00_08_0.text: My monsters work together to form a bridge to victory!

Blackwing - Bombardment!

V0203_08_00_09_0.text: A single Trap will drop all your monsters!

Icarus Attack!

V0203_08_00_12_0.text:
I flip over my Trap Card!
Shadow Impulse!

V0203_08_00_13_0.text:
I reveal my Trap Card!
Defenders Intersect!

V0203_08_00_14_0.text:
This Trap explodes all over ya!
Delta Crow - Anti Reverse!

V0203_08_00_15_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Trap Stun!

V0203_08_00_15_1.text: All other Trap effects are negated this turn!

V0203_08_00_16_0.text: I activate my Trap, Fake Feather!

V0203_08_00_17_0.text: I activate the Trap, Ebon Arrow!

V0203_08_00_18_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Black Thunder!

V0203_08_00_19_0.text: Your best isn't even my least!

V0203_08_00_19_1.text:
I activate my Trap!
Black Sonic!

V0203_08_00_20_0.text:
I flip over my Trap Card!
Blackback!

V0203_08_00_21_0.text:
I reveal my Trap Card!
Blackboost!

V0203_08_00_22_0.text: I was waiting for this moment!

V0203_08_00_22_1.text:
I flip over my Trap Card!
Black Return!

V0203_08_00_23_0.text: I won't let your sacrifice go to waste!

V0203_08_00_23_1.text:
I flip over my Trap Card!
Black Wing Revenge!

V0203_08_00_24_0.text:
Like I'll let you do that!
I activate my Trap, Guard Mines!

V0203_08_00_25_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Level Retuner!

V0203_08_00_27_0.text:
I activate my Trap!

V0203_28_00_00_0.text: Whoever wants it more wins in the end!

V0203_28_00_01_0.text: To stay a hero to them jackals, I'll keep improving my game!

V0203_28_00_02_0.text:
Sorry, pal.
But I knew all your tricks.

V0203_28_00_03_0.text: If you think you can outsmart me, you better think again!

V0203_28_00_04_0.text: I'll lead Team 5D's to the future!

V0203_28_00_06_0.text: I thought about reforming The Enforcers. Whattaya say?

V0203_28_00_07_0.text: If you're gonna hurt innocent kids...

V0203_28_00_07_1.text: You think I'll ever let you off?

V0203_28_00_08_0.text:
Yeah, friends fight sometimes...
But that's not always bad.

V0203_28_00_08_1.text:
Cuz that can bring us closer!
And strengthen our bond!

V0203_29_00_00_0.text:
Aww man...
How am I gonna face the kids?

V0203_29_00_02_0.text: I won't fall for these same tricks next time!

V0203_29_00_03_0.text: You may have broken me this time...

V0203_29_00_03_1.text: But you won't break the bond I have with my pals!

V0203_29_00_04_0.text:
Eh, don't worry about it.
We're still buds.

V0203_29_00_05_0.text: Until the Dark Signers are buried forever, I won't give up!

V0203_29_00_06_0.text: Even if I can't do a thing, I know my friends can!

V0203_29_00_06_1.text: So my defeat will pave the way for my team's victory!

V0203_30_00_00_0.text: I didn't know a Duel could be this dull.

V0203_30_00_01_0.text: C'mon, can't you be more chill?

V0203_33_00_00_0.text: I'll show you moves you've never seen before!

V0203_33_00_02_0.text: When I'm on my game, you don't stand a chance!

V0203_34_00_00_0.text: Enough with those effects! So  not fair!

V0203_34_00_01_0.text: There's nothing fair about that monster!

V0203_34_00_02_0.text: Take those weak tactics outta here!

V0203_34_00_03_0.text: I've been ready to blast ya from the start!

V0203_34_00_04_0.text: Quick moves are my Blackwings' specialty!

V0203_34_00_05_0.text: I miscalculated! I'm losin' my edge!

V0203_34_00_06_0.text: Even if I'm down to 1 LP, my heart has a billion LP!

V0203_34_00_07_0.text: They'll be writing legends about me!

V0203_35_00_00_0.text: Crow will solve all your problems!

V0203_35_00_01_0.text: When Team 5D's needs a win, they turn to me! Crow!

V0203_36_00_02_0.text: Sorry... But I know you can turn this around!

V0203_36_00_03_0.text: Win, Yusei! For all of us!

V0203_36_00_05_0.text: Yusei! As long as you're alive, our bond's forever!

V0203_36_00_07_0.text: I pass the baton to you!

V0203_36_00_08_0.text: Sorry... All hope rests on you!
